aVAccording to Alexander Kluge:
p41
aV"Human beings are not interested in reality.
p42
aVThey can\u2019t be; it\u2019s part of the human essence.
p43
aVThey have desires.
p44
aVThese desires are totally opposed to any form of reality.
p45
aVThey prefer to lie
p46
aVthan to become divorced from their desires."
