aa(lp80
VI remember when I was at NASA in 2009 with 120 engineers.
p81
aVYou guys know, too, when you go up in a plane,
p82
aVthe control panels are gigantic.
p83
aVAnd what we're doing is really complex,
p84
aVand when I started coming in with the plastic bags, saying,
p85
aV"But we have a different way ..."
