aVSeeing the power of this idea,
p88
aVwe started to initiate a new era;
p89
aVone that would leave behind the violence of the Anthropocene
p90
aVand give way to a new era,
p91
aVwhich we call the "Aerocene" \u2014
p92
aVan era of ecological awareness,
p93
aVin which we learn to float together, live together in the air,
