p128
aVthis exact one in my hands,
p129
aVflew 375 miles \u2014 12 hours \u2014 from Germany to Poland,
p130
aVon a fuel-free trip.
p131
aVBut it wasn't free from crossing borders.
p132
aVThe trip was much more complicated than what we imagined;
