aVair space is as regulated and militarized
p134
aVas land space.
p135
aVTo fly using the winds, the heat of the sun
p136
aVand the radiant energy of the earth
p137
aVis complex and beautiful.
p138
aVBut even more complex will be getting the permits
p139
aVto cross the air space of each of the different countries
p140
aVthat we fly over using wind.
